##An emergency meeting was held in Huanggang after 22 people accidentally ate disinfectant tablets

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Zhong Yuhao, reporter, thepaper.cn

According to a report in Huanggang daily on March 3, on March 2, Liu Xuerong, secretary of the Huanggang Municipal Party Committee and Commander of the city's new champion pneumonia epidemic prevention and control work headquarters, presided over an emergency city-wide video conference, the city's current epidemic prevention and control priorities for re-arrangement and re-deployment. Liu Xuerong pointed out that the recent incidents in the prevention and control of the epidemic in Huangmei County have given us a wake-up call, and the whole city should learn from the experience, draw lessons from it and continue to improve its work.

Huangmei County Epidemic Prevention Headquarters earlier reported that at about 9:30 am on February 28, a group of villagers in Xiangyao village, Huangmei town, Huangmei County, 14 households and 22 people mistakenly consumed chlorine dioxide tablets (commonly known as "effervescent tablets") used for environmental disinfection, at a dose of one tablet per person.

On March 1, CCTV news quoted the Government of the People's Republic of China News of Huangmei town in Huangmei County. After investigation, when Huangmei town distributed protective materials to the villages and communities on February 25, they all explained clearly the use of effervescent tablets and how to use them. Each effervescent tablet was mixed with 2 kg of water, for household spray disinfection. Village Women Director, Accountant Luo Xiaohong and grid member Zhai Jinxia are responsible for distributing supplies to the teams. At about 15:00 on the 27th, Luo Xiaohong called a group leader, Jiang Jianjun, to the village committee to collect a group of protective materials and distribute them to the villagers. Jiang Jianjun in the group to do epidemic prevention and persuasion work, then phone the village volunteers Jiang Jinxiong to the village committee to get.

So, Jiang Jinxiong to the village committee from Luo Xiaohong Place will be a group of protective materials. Luo Xiaohong to Jiang Jinxiong said effervescent tablets are used for disinfection after mixing water, 5 per family. After receiving the protective materials, Jiang gave them to Jiang Jianjun at the home of a group of villagers, Jiang Yanan. Jiang Jinxiong believes that the material is Jiang Jianjun informed him from the village committee, should be clear about the use of materials and methods, then did not explain to Jiang Jianjun effervescent tablets use and methods.

At about 9:30 on the 28th, Jiang Jianjun, a group leader in Xiangyao village, Huangmei town, Huangmei County, led the village volunteers, Yu Qiao, Jiang Bing and Jiang Yongxin, as they went door to door for temperature tests, registration and distribution of effervescent tablets, jiang Jianjun thought effervescent tablets were a drug to prevent and treat the new coronavirus without knowing the purpose and method of use. He told villagers to "take one tablet each and swallow it" . Some of the villagers who had swallowed the effervescent tablets reported feeling unwell, jiang Jianjun promptly took back the effervescent tablets he had been given.

At the March 2 meeting, Liu Xuerong stressed that disinfection and sterilization is a very important technical means to interrupt the spread, to be carried out scientifically and normatively. We should strictly manage disinfection drugs, store them in a standard way, use them correctly, disinfect them scientifically, and resolutely put an end to potential safety hazards. We should attach great importance to the management of hospital sense and ensure the supply of adequate and sufficient quantities of protective materials for medical personnel. Relevant medical institutions should earnestly fulfill their main responsibilities and strengthen management in accordance with the regulations and norms, all links of the service staff must be screened to take up posts, to do the work in detail do in place. We should strengthen the prevention and control of prisons, detention centers, drug addiction treatment centers, nursing homes, welfare homes, psychiatric hospitals and other special places, do a good job of prevention and control work plan, do a good job of screening all staff, do a whole closed management, the whole process of control.

Huangmei County Epidemic Prevention Headquarters on March 2,2 at 9:40 am, Huangmei County Huangmei town Xiangyao village, another three villagers healed and discharged. So far, 21 of the 22 villagers who have taken disinfection tablets by mistake have been cured and discharged from hospital, while the other one has been basically cured. However, due to his old age and other basic diseases, he will remain in hospital for observation and treatment for safety reasons.

This issue is edited by Chang Chen
